内容，若内容被投诉或经平台巡检发现存在侵权、抄袭等行为，平台认定属实的，平台将视为严重违反平台规范进行处理，并回收闲鱼玩家头衔。严重违规者还将面临账号扣分、封禁等处罚。","class":"android.view.View","package":"com.taobao.idlefish","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":true,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"isVisibleToUser":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 258 - 393, 394)","boundsInScreen":"(0, 1644 - 1080, 2018)"},{"index":6,"text":"2.通过刷粉、刷单、重复发布同一件商品、重复发布同一篇帖子等作弊行为完成玩家身份认证，平台将回收“闲鱼玩家”头衔。","class":"android.view.View","package":"com.taobao.idlefish","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":true,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"isVisibleToUser":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 393 - 393, 485)","boundsInScreen":"(0, 2015 - 1080, 2268)"},{"index":7,"text":"","class":"android.view.View","package":"com.taobao.idlefish","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":true,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"isVisibleToUser":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 484 - 393, 533)","boundsInScreen":"(0, 2266 - 1080, 2400)","children":[{"index":0,"text":"第三条 【其他】","class":"android.view.View","package":"com.taobao.idlefish","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"isVisibleToUser":false,"boundsInParent":"(20, 48 - 373, 49)","boundsInScreen":"(55, 2398 - 1025, 2400)"}]},{"index":8,"text":"1.本规范为闲鱼社区规则（包括《闲鱼社区公约》、《闲鱼社区管理规范》等）的下位规范。闲鱼社区规则已有规定的，从其规定；未有规定或本规范有特殊规定的，按照本规范执行。","class":"android.view.View","package":"com.taobao.idlefish","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":true,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"isVisibleToUser":false,"boundsInParent":"(0, 532 - 393, 533)","boun